metadataAttributes.Title: Sequence Models
metadataAttributes.Short Intro: In the fifth course of the Deep Learning Specialization, you will become familiar with sequence models and their exciting applications such as speech recognition, music synthesis, chatbots, machine translation, natural language processing (NLP), and more.
